ods reachable in Native Image analysis.\n\nUpdated:\n\n- `tests/src/org.scala-lang/scala-library/2.11.8/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/reachability-metadata.json`\n  - Added `reflection` metadata with `serializable: true` for:\n    - `scala.collection.concurrent.TrieMap`\n    - `scala.collection.concurrent.TrieMapSerializationEnd$`\n    - test helper hashing/equality classes\n  - Explicitly registered `TrieMap.writeObject(ObjectOutputStream)` and `TrieMap.readObject(ObjectInputStream)`.\n  - Kept `serialization` metadata for the same serialization graph.\n\n- `metadata/org.scala-lang/scala-library/2.11.8/reachability-metadata.json`\n  - Added library-level metadata for `TrieMap` serialization.\n  - Registered `writeObject` / `readObject` and the serialization sentinel object.\n\nThe existing dedicated Scala test file remains focused on `scala.collection.concurrent.TrieMap` and continues to exercise serialization/deserialization via public `ObjectOutputStream` / `ObjectInputStream`.\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0052d26d7a30ead30169f51d8fa98c8196a437101612259fd9\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1134, "output": 891, "cacheRead": 66048, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 68073, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777671550178, "responseId": "resp_0052d26d7a30ead30169f51d7edfc08196a287562327f0f421"}}
